Add-On for Theatrum Orbis Terrarum (Carthoge Reloaded) that changes the interface fonts. Can also be used as a standalone mod.

    Ironman and achievement compatible, multiplayer friendly
    Compatible with any mod that doesn't modify the interface or fonts
    Compatible with VD:TGX and similar mods
    Compatible with map font mods 


If you want to use this mod together with Banners 2, use this compatibility patch by Phalanx.
How to make this compatibility patch compatible with the TOT base mod:

    go to your mod folder
    open banners_totif_compatch.zip with 7zip
    open interface\topbar.gui, edit line 726 to
    	text = ""	
    save and close topbar.gui, confirm changes to zip file
